reviewText: Did not get any blue rays. They were all just DVDs. Was such a disappointment. And 2 out of the 4 dvds were scratched.
Actually to good of a show to the point that I'm affended.
My son loves the show.  This is part of his christmas presents.
What a great show!  I can't be more happy to have it on Blu-ray!

Archer is the best.
If you don't like to laugh,
If you don't like ocelots,
If you don't like man on robot relations,
If you don't like amazing spy kick-ass-ery,
then this show isn't for you.
Do you want ants?  Because that's how you get ants.
